major%20offensive%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20which%20will%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarros%20agreed%20that%20if%20Ukraine%20doesn't%20get%20a%20resupply%20of%20weaponry%2C%20it%20will%20ultimately%20concede%20territory.%20And%20it%20won't%20be%20entirely%20the%20fault%20of%20glide%20bombs%20%E2%80%94%20Kyiv%20needs%20all%20the%20tools%20its%20forces%20can%20get%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20all%20things%20keep%20the%20same%20and%20the%20Russians%20keep%20with%20their%20current%20pattern%20of%20innovation%20and%20adaptation%2C%20we%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20doubt%20that%20the%20Russian%20air%20force%20will%20become%20more%20involved%20in%20this%20war%20and%20bring%20more%20forces%20to%20bear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20will%20ultimately%20affect%20the%20ground%20domain%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-in-a-race-to-stop-russia-glide-bomb-attacks-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711530002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660322dc1caec1275a69b0bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-in-a-race-to-stop-russia-glide-bomb-attacks-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20likely%20to%20lose%20more%20ground%20unless%20it%20stops%20the%20glide%20bombs%20launched%20by%20Russian%20aircraft%20that%20are%20hammering%20their%20defenses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-in-a-race-to-stop-russia-glide-bomb-attacks-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20fit%20in%20at%20dinner%20with%20a%20billionaire%2C%20according%20to%20an%20etiquette%20expert%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width