0fit%20with%20a%20large%20TV%2C%20power%20ports%2C%20and%20a%20lie-flat%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20configuration%20ensures%20all%20passengers%20have%20direct%20aisle%20access%2C%20unlike%20those%20on%20Air%20India's%20notoriously%20dated%20business%20class%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20differences%20from%20competitors%20is%20less%20visual.%20Unlike%20many%20airlines%2C%20missing%20from%20SoFab%20is%20buttons%20that%20control%20the%20seat%20and%20bed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20control%20panel%20on%20the%20A350%20business%20class%20seat%2C%20which%20could%20create%20a%20cradle%20position%2C%20but%20not%20fully%20lie%20flat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c60eaebcd21800196b83a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20control%20panel%20on%20Singapore's%20A350%20business-class%20seat.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20class%20has%20evolved%20over%20the%20decades%20to%20have%20lie-flat%20beds%20that%20adjust%20using%20an%20electronic%20panel%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-airways-club-suite-business-class-london-nyc-review-photos-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClub%20Suite%20on%20British%20Airways%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Room%26quot%3B%20on%20All%20Nippon%20Airways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20passengers%20to%20set%20up%20their%20bed%20for%20sleeping.%20However%2C%20Optimares'%20design%20takes%20that%20one%20step%20further%20to%20give%20customers%20even%20more%20space%20to%20lay%20in%20any%20position%2C%20including%20their%20side%2C%20back%2C%20front%2C%20curled%20up%20in%20a%20ball%2C%20or%20fully%20stretched%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20lieu%20of%20the%20heavy%20electronics%20built%20into%20these%20control%20panels%2C%20Opimares%20opted%