ummoned%20Again%20In%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Violation%20Case%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mahua%20Moitra%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20alleged%20foreign%20exchange%20violation%20case%2C%20sources%20said%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20wants%20to%20question%20Ms%20Moitra%20over%20transactions%20linked%20to%20a%20non-resident%20external%2C%20or%20NRE%2C%20account%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20few%20instances%20of%20foreign%20remittances%20and%20transfer%20of%20funds%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency's%20summons%20-%20its%20third%20to%20the%20former%20Krishnanagar%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20-%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20filed%20a%20police%20case%20and%20raided%20her%20Kolkata%20home%20in%20the%20cash-for-query%20case%20that%20led%20to%20Ms%20Moitra's%20hugely%20controversial%20expulsion%20from%20Parliament%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20parliamentary%20ethics%20panel%20found%20Ms%20Moitra's%20conduct%20%26quot%3Bimmoral%20(and)%20indecent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20taking%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%20cash%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20gift%20items%26quot%3B%2C%20from%20a%20businessman%20-%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20-%20to%20ask%20questions%20critical%20of%20the%20government%20in%20Parliament.%20She%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20sharing%20log-in%20details%20to%20her%20confidential%20account%20on%20the%20parliament%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hiranandani%20has%20also%20been%20summoned%20for%20questioning%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20denied%20the%20bribery%20charges%20(but%20said%20she%20did%20share%20website%20credentials%2C%20arguing%20it%20is%20common%20practice%20among%20MPs).%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20hear%20this%20case%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20has%20re-nominated%20Ms%20Moitra%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20Krishnanagar%20seat%20she%20won%20in%20the%202019%20election%3B%20she%20eased%20to%20victory%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20picking%20up%20nearly%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20will%20contest%20Amrita%20Roy%2C%20the%20rajmata%20of%20a%20local%20royal%20family%2C%20whom%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20will%20have%20enough%20sway%20to%20win%20a%20seat%20that%20it%20has%20won%20only%20once%20since%20the%20seat%20first%20voted%20in%201967.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711527720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F261uj8ag_mahua-moitra_650x400_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-summoned-again-in-foreign-exchange-violation-case-sources-5319450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mahua%20Moitra%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20alleged%20foreign%20exchange%20violation%20case%2C%20sources%20said%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-summoned-again-in-foreign-exchange-violation-case-sources-5319450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTurning%20Criminal%20Law%20On%20its%20Head%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Blasts%20Probe%20Agency%20ED%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20challenged%20in%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20related%20to%20the%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%C2%A0The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20has%20passed%20over%20the%20matter%20for%20a%20hearing%20later%20in%20the%20day%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20questioned%20the%20agency's%20%26quot%3Bdelaying%20tactics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%20said%20the%20agency%20got%20a%20copy%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20petition%20only%20yesterday%20and%20sought%20three%20weeks'%20time%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20person%20has%20been%20jail.%20On%20March%2023%2C%20the%20petition%20was%20filed.%20Defects%20were%20cured%20later.%20I%20am%20sure%20Mr%20Raju%20does%20not%20want%20us%20to%20serve%20the%20defective%20copy%20to%20him.%20Defects%20were%20cleared%20late%20last%20night%20and%20we%20shared%20the%20petition%20with%20him%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sharma%20then%20said%20she%20will%20seek%20a%20reply%20and%20give%20a%20short%20date%20for%20the%20hearing%20on%20interim%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20he%20has%20challenged%20the%20remand%20that%20ends%20tomorrow.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20asking%20the%20ladyship%20to%20decide%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20remand.%20That%20requires%20no%20reply%20from%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20delaying%20tactics%2C%20I%20am%20asking%20my%20ladyships%20to%20decide%20it%20today.%20There%20are%20weighty%20reasons%20why%20a%20matter%20which%20challenges%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20remand%20requires%20a%20hearing%20today.%20It%20is%20my%20ladyship's%20prerogative%20to%20allow%20it%20or%20deny%20it.%20My%20ladyship%20may%20take%20a%20call%20on%20that.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20reply%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20in%20his%20petition%20that%20his%20arrest%20violated%20his%20human%20rights%20and%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20crime.%20%26quot%3BArrest%20without%20interrogation%20shows%20that%20the%20current%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said%2C%20demanding%20immediate%20release%20from%20jail%20and%20cancellation%20of%20remand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20said%20it%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20later%20in%20the%20day%20after%20finishing%20the%20supplementary%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20started%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20ED's%20request%20for%20three%20weeks'%20time%20is%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20mala%20fide%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BEven%20one%20day%20incarceration%20is%20an%20issue%20of%20fundamental%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20strange%20situation%20of%20a%20sitting%20CM%20arrested%20on%20a%20summons%20issued%20in%20October%20without%20any%20statement%20under%20Section%2050%20and%20non-existent%20inquiry.%20The%20object%20of%20the%20arrest%20is%20very%20different.%20It%20is%20to%20create%20a%20non-level%20playing%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20hitting%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20heart%20of%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20ED%20arrests%20a%20person%2C%20who%20suffers%20in%20jail%20and%20is%20then%20made%20to%20apply%20for%20bail.%20%26quot%3BNext%20step%2C%20the%20ASG%20tells%20the%20court%20I%20have%20no%20opposition%20to%20bail.%20The%20reason%20cited%20is%20he%20has%20back%20pain.%20The%20next%20step%20is%2C%20he%20comes%20out%20and%20makes%20a%20statement%20against%20me.%20Next%20he%20turns%20approver%20and%20is%20granted%20pardon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20happened%20in%20every%20case%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20It%20is%20blowing%20to%20smithereens%20the%20constitutional%20safeguards%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20no%20corroboration%20of%20these%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20an%20approver%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20untrustworthy%20friend%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20species%20called%20approver...%20In%20our%20history%2C%20whether%20for%20good%20motives%20or%20bad%20motives%2C%20the%20courts%20have%20dealt%20with%20phrases%20like%20Jaichand%20and%20Trojan%20Horses.%20The%20history%20looks%20very%20harshly%20at%20these%20Jaichands%20and%20Trojan%20horses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20ED's%20counsel%20SV%20Raju%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20file%20replies%20on%20the%20main%20matter%20and%20on%20the%20petition%20for%20interim%20relief.%20When%20the%20court%20said%20it%20has%20already%20said%20that%20it%20will%20issue%20notice%20in%20the%20main%20matter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20interim%20relief%20also%2C%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%20If%20I%20am%20not%20entitled%20to%20file%20a%20reply%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20hear%20me.%20I%20can't%20be%20deprived%20of%20my%20right%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20said%20it%20will%20pass%20and%20order%20by%204%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20relief.%20However%2C%20he%20later%20withdrew%20his%20petition%20and%20his%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20said%20they%20would%20contest%20the%20remand%20proceedings%20before%20the%20trial%20court%20and%20return%20to%20the%20top%20court%20with%20another%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20he%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%2C%20which%20remanded%20him%20in%20a%20weeklong%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20money%20laundering%20case%20is%20based%20on%20a%20case%20registered%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20in%202022%20that%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20case%2C%20registered%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Delhi's%20Centre-appointed%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20alleges%20that%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20intentionally%20left%20loopholes%20in%20the%20policy%20to%20favour%20some%20licensees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20alleges%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20a%20key%20conspirator%20in%20the%20case.%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20such%20as%20ED%20and%20CBI%20for%20political%20motives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20trying%20to%20prevent%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20from%20campaigning%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20continue%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20AAP%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20have%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20issuing%20orders%20from%20the%20ED's%20lock-up%20and%20assured%20Delhi%20residents%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20constantly%20thinking%20about%20their%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711527660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fseblkpqo_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-enforcement-directorate-delhi-high-court-to-hear-arvind-kejriwals-petition-against-arrest-5318028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20hear%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20challenge%20to%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20last%20week%20and%20a%20trial%20court's%20order%20that%20remanded%20him%20in%20the%20agency's%20custody%20for%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n