r%20put%20the%20amount%20of%20money%2C%20which%20was%20paid%20by%20people%20in%20the%20state%20as%20bribe%20for%20getting%20jobs%2C%20at%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20her%20to%20inform%20people%20about%20his%20stand%20and%20asserted%20that%20soon%20after%20coming%20back%20to%20power%20he%20will%20find%20a%20way%2C%20including%20making%20legal%20provisions%20if%20needed%2C%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20support%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20following%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%2C%20saying%20those%20who%20made%20complaint%20against%20the%20AAP%20have%20now%20changed%20tack%20to%20help%20it.%20He%2C%20though%2C%20did%20not%20name%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shows%20that%20their%20priority%20is%20not%20country%20but%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20is%20fighting%20for%20a%20corruption-free%20country%20for%20the%20bright%20future%20of%20the%20youth%20while%20all%20the%20corrupt%20have%20come%20together%20on%20the%20other%20side%20to%20save%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Roy%20tracing%20her%20lineage%20to%2018th%20century%20local%20king%20Krishnachandra%20Roy%2C%20PM%20Modi%20hit%20back%20at%20those%20who%20have%20targeted%20the%20erstwhile%20royalty%20for%20its%20alleged%20support%20to%20the%20British%20after%20the%20BJP%20named%20her%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20Modi%20that%20her%20family%20is%20being%20called%20traitors%20and%20noted%20that%20Krishnachandra%20Roy%20worked%20for%20people%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20other%20kings%20to%20save%20%26quot%3BSanatan%20Dharma%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20her%20to%20not%20take%20any%20pressure%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20(TMC)%20practice%20vote%20bank%20politics%20and%20will%20make%20all%20kinds%20of%20wild%20allegations.%20They%20do%20so%20to%20hide%20their%20sins%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%20they%20seek%20evidence%20of%20Lord%20Ram's%20existence%20while%20on%20the%20other%20they%20cite%20incidents%20dating%20back%20to%20two%20and%20three%20centuries%20to%20defame%20others%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20their%20double%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said%2C%20praising%20the%20king's%20legacy%20of%20social%20reforms%20and%20development%20and%20asking%20her%20to%20carry%20forward%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20confidence%20of%20her%20win%2C%20he%20asked%20Roy%20to%20be%20ready%20with%20the%20agenda%20for%20the%20first%20100%20days%20for%20her%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20West%20Bengal%20will%20vote%20for%20%26quot%3BParivartan%26quot%3B%20(change)%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20corruption%20of%20the%20state's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20planks%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%2C%20as%20it%20has%20highlighted%20the%20arrest%20of%20some%20of%20them%2C%20including%20former%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20and%20recovery%20of%20large%20amounts%20of%20money%20and%20other%20assets%20from%20them%20to%20target%20its%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20challenge%20to%20save%20Bengal's%20heritage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20people%20have%20expressed%20their%20confidence%20in%20the%20Modi%20government's%20work%20and%20told%20her%20that%20Moitra%2C%20the%20incumbent%20TMC%20MP%20from%20the%20constituency%2C%20will%20go%20to%20jail%2C%20drawing%20laugher%20from%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoitra%20is%20facing%20probe%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20for%20allegedly%20allowing%20a%20businessman%20to%20use%20her%20parliamentary%20log-in%20in%20return%20of%20bribe%20and%20other%20favours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20termed%20the%20businessman%20