he%20turned%20to%20manifestation%20while%20reading%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Secret%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20hoping%20for%20a%20pregnancy%20after%20struggling%20to%20conceive%20naturally.%20Farah%20said%20that%20she%20and%20Shirish%20had%20already%20chosen%20names%20for%20their%20children%20before%20learning%20they%20were%20expecting%20triplets.%20She%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BMe%20and%20Shirish%20started%20talking%20about%20kids%20and%20what%20we%20want%20to%20name%20them%20and%20how%20they%20will%20be%20and%20all%20that.%20When%20the%20doctor%20called%20I%20was%20100%20percent%20sure%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20be%20pregnant%20and%20she%20said%2C%20'Listen%2C%20Farah%2C%20don't%20jump%20too%20high%2C%20I%20want%20you%20to%20be%20calm%2C%20you%20are%20pregnant%20but%20don't%20get%20your%20hopes%20up%20but%20it%20is%20multiple%20pregnancies'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fananya-pandays-video-with-her-frenemy-farah-khan-is-major-lol-5282189%5C%22%3EFarah%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20recounted%20the%20shock%20of%20discovering%20her%20multiple%20pregnancies%20and%20the%20difficult%20decision%20she%20faced%20due%20to%20her%20age.%20Advised%20by%20her%20doctor%20to%20%26quot%3Breduce%26quot%3B%20one%20child%20because%20of%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20her%20age%2C%20Farah%20said%20that%20she%20bravely%20chose%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20triplets%20and%20delivered%20her%20three%20bundles%20of%20joy%20-%20Czar%2C%20Anya%2C%20and%20Diva%20in%202008.%20%26quot%3BAt%20ten%20days%20she%20(the%20doctor)%20called%20me%20and%20she%20said%20that%20it's%20triplets%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'Haan%2C%20I%20just%20knew%20it%20doc'.%20Of%20course%20we%20were%20too%20excited%20and%20the%20doctor%20gave%20us%20a%20reality%20check%20and%20said%20that%20we'd%20have%20to%20reduce%20one%20because%20normally%20most%20twins%20start%20out%20as%20triplets.%20She%20said%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20be%2043%20when%20the%20children%20come%20and%20it's