osh%20Amid%20Row%20Over%20Remarks%20On%20Mamata%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%20over%20his%20offensive%20remark%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20today%20launched%20a%20counterstrike%20on%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20Abhishek%20and%20questioned%20his%20comments%20on%20BJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20is%20a%20man%2C%20he%20and%20his%20father%20%5Bformer%20MP%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Sisir%20Adhikari%5D%20don't%20have%20any%20respect%3F%20A%20woman%20card%20is%20being%20used%20frequently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20Ms%20Banerjee%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20%26quot%3BDidi%20goes%20to%20Goa%20and%20says%2C%20'I%20am%20Goa's%20daughter'%2C%20then%20goes%20to%20Tripura%20and%20says%2C%20'I%20am%20Tripura's%20daughter'.%20Decide%20who%20your%20father%20is.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20to%20be%20just%20anybody's%20daughter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20came%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20video%20and%20said%20Mr%20Ghosh's%20remarks%20show%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bzero%20respect%26quot%3B%20for%20women.%20Party%20leaders%20also%20said%20his%20remarks%20reflect%20frustration%20over%20being%20moved%20from%20the%20Medinipur%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20currently%20represents%2C%20to%20Bardhaman%20Durgapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20left%20the%20BJP%20red-faced%20and%20provided%20fodder%20to%20the%20Opposition%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20corner%20the%20Congress%20over%20offensive%20social%20media%20posts%20from%20the%20profile%20of%20its%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shrinate%20has%20said%20the%20derogatory%20posts%20on%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20were%20made%20without%20her%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Trinamool%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20over%20Mr%20Ghosh's%20remarks%2C%20the%20party%20leadership%20demanded%20an%20explanation%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh%20has%20said%20he%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20party's%20questions.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20controversy%20has%20erupted%20over%20my%20remarks.%20I%20have%20no%20personal%20enmity%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20I%20have%20only%20questioned%20the%20political%20remarks%20she%20has%20made%20to%20mislead%20people.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20problems%20with%20my%20language%20and%20usage%20of%20words.%20My%20party%20has%20also%20pointed%20it%20out.%20Many%20have%20said%20it%20is%20unparliamentary.%20If%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20I%20regret%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20have%20a%20question.%20A%20leader%20from%20her%20party%2C%20her%20family%2C%20has%20said%20worse%20things%20about%20the%20leader%20of%20BJP's%20legislative%20party%20(Suvendu%20Adhikari)%20and%20his%20father.%20Don't%20they%20have%20any%20respect%3F%20His%20father%20is%20a%20senior%20politician%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%20did%20not%20protest%20then.%20Why%20didn't%20they%20issue%20a%20statement%3F%20I%20have%20made%20a%20political%20statement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20Trinamool's%20national%20general%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20has%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20launched%20scathing%20attacks%20on%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20left%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20the%20Trinamool%20repeating%20Krishnanagar%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20as%20a%20candidate%20but%20not%20naming%20her%20a%20star%20campaigner%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20their%20party's%20business.%20They%20can't%20find%20candidates%2C%20so%20they%20are%20getting%20tainted%20people%20and%20going%20as%20far%20as%20Gujarat.%20The%20public%20will%20decide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnanagar%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20a%20rich%20heritage.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20land%20of%20Chaitanya%20Mahaprabhu.%20And%20the%20MP%20representing%20that%20seat%20says%20whatever%20she%20wants%20in%20Parliament%20and%20then%20gets%20suspended.%20I%20have%20said%20nothing%20(compared%20to%20her).%20Will%20people%20vote%20for%20her%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711521360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fk9j9hoeo_dilip-ghosh-mamata-banerjee_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdilip-ghosh-mamata-banerjee-woman-card-bjps-dilip-ghosh-amid-row-over-remarks-on-mamata-banerjee-5318939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20row%20over%20his%20offensive%20remark%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20today%20launched%20a%20counterstrike%20on%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20Abhishek%20and%20questioned%20his%20comments%20on%20BJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20and%20his%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdilip-ghosh-mamata-banerjee-woman-card-bjps-dilip-ghosh-amid-row-over-remarks-on-mamata-banerjee-5318939%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Green%20Energy%20commissions%20180MW%20solar%20plant%20at%20Devikot%2C%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711521129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-02%2F02%2Ffull%2F1486058910-5009.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-green-energy-commissions-180mw-solar-plant-at-devikot-rajasthan-124032700296_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22