s%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603b0631caec1275a69c5f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeft%3A%20The%20cargo%20ship%20Dali%20sits%20in%20the%20water%20after%20running%20into%20and%20collapsing%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%2C%20Right%3A%20Security%20forces%20take%20measures%20and%20close%20the%20roads%20leading%20to%20the%20collapsed%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%3Cp%3ECelal%20Gunes%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%20and%20Tasos%20Katopodis%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERadio%20archives%20show%20police%20had%20less%20than%20two%20minutes%20to%20close%20traffic%20at%20a%20bridge%20before%20its%20collapse.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bridge%20in%20Baltimore%20fell%20into%20the%20Patapsco%20River%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20a%20984-foot%20ship%20crashed%20into%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAuthorities%20credited%20the%20officers%20with%20saving%20lives%20by%20quickly%20stopping%20cars%20from%20crossing%20the%20bridge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn-site%20officers%20from%20the%20Maryland%20Transportation%20Authority%20Police%20had%20less%20than%20two%20minutes%20to%20halt%20traffic%20on%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%20before%20a%20container%20ship%20crashed%20into%20its%20support%20beam%2C%20dispatch%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20say%20the%20Dali%2C%20a%20984-foot%20Singapore-flagged%20vessel%2C%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-collapse-cargo-ship-mayday-call-traffic-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emayday%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20lost%20power%20while%20bearing%20down%20on%20the%20bridge%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20call%20and%20the%20subsequent%20actions%20of%20law%20enforcement%20to%20quickly%20seal%20off%20traffic%20on%20the%20bridge%20have%20been%20credited%20with%20preventing%20further%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArchives%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.broadcastify.com%2Fcalls%2Ftg%2F7214%2F7101%2Farchives%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolice%20radio%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Broadcastify%2C%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20show%20just%20how%20little%20time%20some%20officers%20had%20to%20react%20before%20the%20ship's%20impact%20collapsed%20the%20bridge.%20Part%20of%20the%20archives%20can%20be%20listened%20to%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRkjZImSG7j4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBroadcastify's%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20easier%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20officers%20communicated%20normally%20until%20one%20alerted%20his%20colleagues%20to%20the%20incoming%20danger%20at%20around%201.27%20a.m.%20that%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20one%20of%20you%20guys%20on%20the%20south%20side%2C%20one%20of%20you%20guys%20on%20the%20north%20side.%20Hold%20all%20traffic%20on%20the%20key%20bridge%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20ship%20approaching%20that's%20just%20lost%20their%20steering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20officers%20responded%20affirmatively%20within%2020%20seconds%20and%20said%20they%20were%20moving%20to%20follow%20his%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20another%20officer%20raised%20a%20new%20issue.%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20a%20crew%20working%20on%20the%20bridge%20right%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20small%20construction%20crew%20of%20eight%20workers%20was%20fixing%20potholes%20on%20the%20bridge%2C%20and%20six%20of%20them%20are%20now%20presumed%20dead.%20The%20six%20were%20Latino%20and%20were%20having%20a%20meal%20break%20in%20or%20near%20their%20vehicles%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crash%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2024%2F03%2F26%2Fbaltimore-bridge-collapse-key-ship-crash%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20their%20colleagues%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%201%3A28%20a.m.%2C%20t