%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bholistic%20approach%26quot%3B%20to%20build%20its%20devices%20and%20experiences%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20era%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20this%20change%2C%20we%20are%20bringing%20together%20the%20Windows%20Experiences%20and%20Windows%20%2B%20Devices%20teams%20as%20a%20core%20part%20of%20the%20Experiences%20%2B%20Devices%20(E%2BD)%20division.%20This%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20take%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20building%20silicon%2C%20systems%2C%20experiences%2C%20and%20devices%20that%20span%20Windows%20client%20and%20cloud%20for%20this%20AI%20era.%20Pavan%20Davuluri%20will%20lead%20this%20team%20and%20continue%20to%20report%20to%20me.%20Shilpa%20Ranganathan%20and%20Jeff%20Johnson%20and%20their%20teams%20will%20report%20directly%20to%20Pavan.%20The%20Windows%20team%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20Microsoft%20AI%20team%20on%20AI%2C%20silicon%2C%20and%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Davuluri%20has%20worked%20for%20over%2023%20years%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20its%20work%20with%20Qualcomm%20and%20AMD%20to%20create%20processors%20for%20Surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20excited%20for%20this%20team%20to%20help%20Microsoft%20AI%20achieve%20its%20bold%20ambition%20to%20build%20world-class%20consumer%20AI%20products.%20And%20I%20very%20much%20look%20forward%20to%20closely%20partnering%20with%20Mustafa%20and%20the%20team%20as%20we%20bring%20our%20AI%20products%2C%20including%20Copilot%2C%20to%20the%20breadth%20of%20our%20E%2BD%20products%20and%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reorganisation%20announcement%20comes%20days%20after%20Google%20DeepMind%20co-founder%20and%20former%20Inflection%20AI%20CEO%20Mustafa%20Suleyman%20joined%20Microsoft%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20its%20new%20AI%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711515420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-0