Opinion%3A%20Muslim%20Leaders%20And%20The%20Languages%20They%20Employ%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.ndtv.com%2Falbums%2FNEWS%2Fpics-eid-celebr_637871672690863546%2F637871672719666544.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20'Muslim%20vote%20bank%2C'%20commonly%20used%20to%20discuss%20the%20dynamics%20of%20Muslim%20politics%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20lost%20its%20currency.%20Apart%20from%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leaders%2C%20who%20invoke%20'vote%20bank%20politics'%20to%20criticise%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20for%20their%20perceived%20leniency%20towards%20Muslims%2C%20few%20discuss%20it%20these%20days.%20The%20assumption%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Muslims%20think%20and%20vote%20strategically%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20particular%20party%20or%20coalition%20persists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20normalisation%20of%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20bank%20as%20the%20ultimate%20political%20truth%20of%20Muslim%20politics%20is%20a%20result%20of%20increasing%20political%20polarisation.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20demonises%20Muslims%20to%20assert%20its%20Hindutva-driven%20nationalism.%20Instead%20of%20engaging%20in%20a%20meaningful%20discussion%20about%20the%20evolving%20political%20aspirations%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20Modi%20era%2C%20this%20section%20relies%20heavily%20on%20prevalent%20political%20stereotypes%20associated%20with%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpponents%20of%20Hindutva%20reject%20this%20negative%20portrayal%20of%20Muslims%20and%20decry%20this%20overt%20communalisation.%20However%2C%20their%20critique%20of%20pro-Hindutva%20media%20is%20based%20on%20an%20equally%20problematic%20assertion.%20They%20want%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20an%20anti-Muslim%20party%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20Muslims%20always%20participate%20in%20elections%20to%20defeat%20it.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20a%20closed%2C%20one-dimensional%2C%20and%20homogeneous%20Muslim%20identity%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20Muslim%20politics%2C%20is%20perpetuated%20and%20sustained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20rigid%20concepts%20about%20Muslim%20politics%20are%20deeply%20troubling.%20It%20is%20undeniable%20that%20Muslim%20identity%20has%20become%20a%20problematic%20category%20in%20recent%20years.%20Increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Muslims-such%20as%20riots%2C%20lynching%2C%20and%20attacks%20on%20places%20of%20worship%20(and%20worshippers!)-at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20have%20influenced%20Muslim%20self-perception%20as%20a%20minority.%20Simultaneously%2C%20the%20portrayal%20of%20Islam%20as%20antithetical%20to%20Indian%2FHindu%20civilisation%20has%20challenged%20the%20secular%20consensus%20regarding%20the%20Indianness%20of%20Muslims.%20Yet%2C%20it%20would%20be%20entirely%20inappropriate%20to%20make%20sweeping%20generalisations%20about%20the%20relevance%20of%20Muslim%20politics%20in%20contemporary%20times.%20There%20is%20a%20pressing%20need%20to%20observe%20and%20identify%20the%20emerging%20discourses%20of%20politics%20that%20Muslim%20leaders%20employ%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20state%20at%20various%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETypes%20of%20Muslim%20Leaders%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20comprehensive%20understanding%20of%20the%20term%20'Muslim%20politics'%2C%20we%20must%20differentiate%20between%20Muslim%20leaders%20and%20the%20Muslim%20masses.%20Initial%20findings%20from%20my%20ongoing%20project%20on%20Muslim%20Leadership%20in%20India%20suggest%20that%20there%20are%20three%20types%20of%20Muslim%20leaders%3A%20professional%20Muslim%20politicians%2C%20Muslim%20elites%2C%20and%20Muslim%20activists%2Finfluencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessional%20Muslim%20politicians%20engage%20in%20party%20politics%2C%20operating%20within%20the%20organisational%20structures%20of%20political%20parties%20as%20workers%2C%20office-bearers%2C%20and%20political%20aspirants.%20Many%20of%20them%20secure%20tickets%20to%20contest%20elections%2C%20aspiring%20to%20become%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20(MPs)%2C%20Members%20of%20Legislative%20Assembly%20(MLAs)%2C%20and%20corporators%20in%20local%20civic%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20elites%20are%20individuals%20who%20assert%20their%20leadership%20status%20based%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20and%20educational%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20activists%20play%20a%20distinct%20leadership%20role%2C%20mobilising%20and%2For%20influencing%20the%20Muslim%20community%20on%20specific%20issues.%20With%20the%20proliferation%20of%20social%20media%2C%20the%20number%20of%20online%20Muslim%20influencers%20has%20significantly%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Languages%20of%20Politics%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessional%20Muslim%20politicians%20adhere%20to%20the%20party%20line%2C%20utilising%20the%20official%20stance%20of%20their%20party%20on%20Muslim%20issues%20to%20make%20politically%20relevant%20statements%20in%20public%20life.%20Assuming%20a%20representative%20role%2C%20these%20politicians%20often%20claim%20to%20provide%20political%20advice%20to%20community%20members.%20Relevant%20arguments%20are%20put%20forth%20by%20Muslim%20leaders%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20who%20use%20the%20party's%20slogan%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Esabka%20sath%2C%20sabka%20vikas%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(together%20with%20all%2C%20development%20for%20all)%20to%20convince%20Muslims%20that%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20is%20the%20optimal%20choice%20for%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fsix-reasons-muslims-look-again-modi-2024-polls-9137422%2F%5C%22%3EAn%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20BJP's%20National%20Vice%20President%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20illustrates%20this%20point.%20Mansoor%20does%20not%20assert%20himself%20as%20a%20Muslim%20representative%20but%20rather%20advises%20Muslims%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20a%20professional%20BJP%20politician%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20Muslim.%20This%20example%20underscores%20how%20professional%20Muslim%20politicians%20adapt%20their%20language%20of%20representation%20according%20to%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20elites%20prioritise%20community%20interests%20as%20a%20political%20resource%20to%20develop%20a%20language%20of%20protection.%20The%20inflexible%20stance%20of%20the%20All-India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(AIMPLB)%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20triple%20talaq%20exemplifies%20this%20approach.%20Despite%20the%20practice%20of%20triple%20talaq%20being%20viewed%20as%20a%20social%20evil%20among%20Hanafi%20Sunni%20Muslims%2C%20the%20Muslim%20religious%20elite%2C%20particularly%20the%20AIMPLB%2C%20largely%20disregarded%20this%20social%20concern%20even%20after%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20controversy%20in%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20portrayed%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20as%20a%20divine%20entity%20safeguarding%20the%20collective%20religious%20interests%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20This%20entrenched%20protection%20of%20personal%20law%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Shariat%20emerged%20as%20a%20defined%20elite%20strategy.%20Their%20stance%20remains%20unchanged%20even%20after%20the%20criminalisation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taylorfrancis.com%2Fchapters%2Fedit%2F10.4324%2F9781003211884-8%2Fmuslim-personal-law-triple-talaq-nazima-parveen%5C%22%3Etriple%20talaq%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20serious%20government%20considerations%20regarding%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fnews-analysis%2Fstory%2Ftriple-talaq-laws-supreme-court-muslim-wives-polygamy-husband-abandoning-wives-2395694-2023-06-21%5C%22%3EThis%20persistence%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicates%20the%20AIMPLB's%20reluctance%20to%20abandon%20the%20language%20of%20protection%2C%20which%20serves%20to%20uphold%20their%20status%20as%20religious%20elites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20category%20of%20Muslim%20activists%2Finfluencers%20is%20so%20vast%20that%20making%20definitive%20statements%20about%20their%20functions%20is%20nearly%20impossible.%20These%20activists%20encompass%20various%20types%2C%20each%20with%20distinct%20and%20sometimes%20contradictory%20ideological%20orientations.%20However%2C%20they%20share%20a%20common%20thread%20that%20binds%20them%20together%3A%20a%20language%20of%20struggle%20and%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20language%20befits%20their%20roles%20as%20activists%20and%20influencers%2C%20rendering%20them%20relevant%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%20It%20does%20not%20derive%20from%20any%20specific%20ideological%20framework%20but%20emerges%20as%20a%20response%20to%20critical%20political%20issues.%20The%20anti-Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20protest%20serves%20as%20a%20prime%20example.%20Activists%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%20united%20to%20oppose%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20each%20bringing%20their%20own%20assessments%2C%20arguments%2C%20and%20positions.%20Despite%20these%20differences%2C%20the%20language%20of%20struggle%20and%20resistance%20provided%20them%20with%20a%20context-specific%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20categorisation%20of%20Muslim%20leaders%20lacks%20rigid%20boundaries%20but%20offers%20insight%20into%20the%20complexity%20and%20multifaceted%20nature%20of%20contemporary%20Indian%20Muslim%20politics.%20A%20professional%20Muslim%20politician%20may%20hail%20from%20an%20elite%20background%2C%20or%20they%20may%20also%20function%20as%20an%20influencer%20in%20certain%20contexts.%20Similarly%2C%20an%20activist%2Finfluencer%20might%20transition%20into%20a%20professional%20politician%20over%20time.%20The%20positioning%20and%20role%20of%20a%20Muslim%20leader%20warrant%20serious%20consideration%20to%20grasp%20the%20political%20language%20they%20employ.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20notion%20of%20a%20homogeneous%20Muslim%20political%20identity%20is%20rendered%20meaningless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Hilal%20Ahmed%20is%20Associate%20Professor%2C%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711514460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.ndtv.com%2Falbums%2FNEWS%2Fpics-eid-celebr_637871672690863546%2F637871672719666544.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmuslim-leaders-and-the-languages-they-employ-5318290%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20a%20comprehensive%20understanding%20of%20the%20term%20'Muslim%20politics'%2C%20we%20must%20differentiate%20between%20Muslim%20leaders%20and%20the%20Muslim%20masses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmuslim-leaders-and-the-languages-they-employ-5318290%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%3A%20Sensex%20soars%20500%20pts%3B%20RIL%2C%20Maruti%20shine%3B%20IT%20shares%20slip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711514425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F10%2Ffull%2F1681113155-9159.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-march-27-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-gift-todays-market-news-124032700094_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20Update%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2027%3A%20In%20the%20broader%20market%2C%20the%20BSE%20MidCap%20index%20advanced%200.5%25%2C%20while%20the%20SmallCap%20gained%200.7%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-liv