.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQtBxwkR_spo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20blackout%2C%20the%20Dali%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20momentary%20loss%20of%20propulsion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Maritime%20and%20Port%20Authority%20of%20Singapore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpa.gov.sg%2Fmedia-centre%2Fdetails%2Finvestigators-from-the-transport-safety-investigation-bureau-and-mpa-are-making-their-way-to-baltimore--maryland%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20report%20from%20Synergy%20Marine%2C%20the%20ship's%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20ship%20was%20flagged%20in%20June%20for%20an%20issue%20related%20to%20its%20propulsion%20system%2C%20according%20to%20records%20from%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapcis.tmou.org%2Fpublic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20database%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20port%20controls%20in%20Asia%20Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20still%20unclear%20if%20the%20deficiency%20found%20in%20June%20was%20at%20all%20related%20to%20what%20caused%20the%20crash%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20reported%20in%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Chile%20on%20June%2027%2C%20and%20listed%20as%20a%20propulsion%20and%20auxiliary%20system%20deficiency.%20An%20attached%20note%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BGauges%2C%20thermometers%2C%20etc.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20records%2C%20this%20problem%20was%20not%20deemed%20as%20grounds%20for%20the%20ship%20to%20be%20detained%20in%20Chile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClay%20Diamond%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20American%20Pilots'%20Association%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2024%2F03%2F26%2Fpilot-anchor-turn-baltimore-bridge-collapse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Dali%20lost%20power%20at%20around%201%3A20%20a.m.%2C%20around%20eight%20minu