%20whom%20are%20students%2C%20unemployed%20youth%20and%20the%20poor%2C%20for%20whom%20every%20rupee%20matters.%20Some%20people%20have%20posted%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220724041558%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsanket_sirsat%2Fstatus%2F1550877329810792448%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220826054520%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsatya2192%2Fstatus%2F1534433423753785344%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%20that%20their%20account%20balance%20has%20gone%20into%20negative%20because%20of%20these%20unauthorised%20and%20unplanned%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20these%20unauthorised%20debits%20can%20be%20ascertained%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20YouTube%20videos%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCfK0MTHVTAQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5ByLGllXPHk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNJo1bN5NgOk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%20about%20how%20to%20exit%20these%20schemes%20garner%20lakhs%20of%20views%20and%20hundreds%20of%20angry%20comments%20from%20aggrieved%20bank%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Canara%20Bank%20customer%20from%20Karnataka%20is%20suing%20the%20bank%20for%20debiting%20his%20account%20without%20consent%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%20In%20a%20case%20filed%20with%20Dharwad%20district%20consumer%20forum%20last%20July%2C%20Kiran%20M%20Goli%20sought%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20damages%20for%20breach%20of%20fiduciary%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoli%20told%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0over%20a%20phone%20call%20that%20the%20bank%20offered%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20outside%20the%20court%20for%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20an%20offer%20he%20rejected.%20He%20said%20he%20is%20pursuing%20the%20case%20not%20for%20money%20but%20for%20drawing%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%20this%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20planned%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20request%20a%20forensic%20audit%20into%20all%20banks%E2%80%99%20enrolment%20modalities%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoli%20said%20Canara%20Bank%20granted%20him%20a%20refund%20for%20unsolicited%20insurance.%20The%20bank%20reportedly%20told%20him%20it%20intended%20to%20debit%20somebody%20else%E2%80%99s%20account%20but%20his%20account%20was%20charged%20because%20of%20a%20technical%20error.%20The%20bank%20gave%20the%20same%20explanation%20to%20another%20customer%20from%20Rajasthan%20who%20had%20filed%20an%20RTI%20request%20in%20July%202023%20to%20ask%20how%20his%20account%20got%20charged%20for%20these%20schemes.%20The%20bank%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20reply%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20some%20technical%20error%2C%20your%20account%20was%20debited%20for%20some%20amount%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20account.%20The%20deduction%20was%20totally%20a%20technical%20error.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20lines%2C%20SBI%20replied%20to%20an%20RTI%20query%20of%20a%20Bihar%20resident%20last%20June%20by%20saying%20that%20his%20account%20was%20debited%20for%20PMJJBY%20erroneously.%20This%20reporter%20knows%20of%20banks%20giving%20the%20same%20reply%20to%20other%20customers%E2%80%99%20RTI%20requests%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20584px)%2085vw%2C%20584px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162739%2F5-SBI-RTI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22584%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22h