the%20bank%20employee%20can%20be%20heard%20requesting%20the%20student%20to%20accept%20the%20money%20and%20let%20go%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20or%20else%20the%20employee%20would%20be%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire.%20The%20student%20refused%20to%20accept%20money%20from%20the%20employee%20and%20insisted%20that%20the%20bank%20refund%20him%2C%20a%20request%20that%20was%20ultimately%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBank%20employees%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20the%20unrelenting%20pressure%20to%20add%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20has%20been%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20them.%20Refusing%20to%20enrol%20customers%20through%20easy%20but%20illegal%20methods%20can%20earn%20the%20ire%20of%20seniors%20whereas%20a%20complaint%20of%20wrongful%20enrolment%20from%20a%20customer%20can%20be%20a%20blot%20on%20their%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%2026%20April%202023%2C%20more%20than%2016.19%20crore%20people%20stood%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1922622%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubscribed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20PMJJBY%20and%20more%20than%2034.18%20crore%20stood%20subscribed%20to%20PMSBY.%20Bank%20employees%20contend%20that%20if%20a%20forensic%20audit%20is%20undertaken%2C%20most%20of%20these%20registrations%20will%20turn%20out%20to%20have%20been%20done%20without%20customers%E2%80%99%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHemant%20Gairola%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20based%20in%20Dehradun.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fbanks-want-forged-paper-trails-after-taking-money-illegally-from-customers-for-modi-govt-s-flagship-schemes-66020a2da1d42%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20Article%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711503047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105750%2F1166496076_ac2efae0