0and%20the%20villa%20is%20full%20of%20paintings%20given%20to%20us%20by%20our%20guests%20from%20the%20artist%20retreats.%20Before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20Wi-Fi%20at%20the%20property.%20We%20left%20a%20note%20for%20our%20guests%20to%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20and%20have%20a%20true%20off-the-grid%20experience%20without%20any%20internet.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20television%20even%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Prachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20stay%20at%20Avabodha%2C%20what%20you%20wake%20up%20to%20are%20the%20misty%20hills%2C%20the%20chirping%20of%20insects%2C%20and%20bird%20songs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20peacocks%20and%20birds%20coming%20into%20our%20garden%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20do%20not%20allow%20pets%20at%20the%20property%20currently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20has%20three%20bedrooms%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hall%20and%20a%20kitchen%20along%20with%20a%20bonfire%20area%2C%20a%20hammock%20area%2C%20and%20a%20garden.%20The%20cost%20of%20staying%20varies%20based%20on%20factors%20like%20weekends%2C%20tourist%20seasons%2C%20and%20holidays.%20On%20average%2C%20the%20entire%20villa%20costs%20Rs%2021%2C000%20per%20night%2C%20shares%20Alka%2C%20and%20the%20couples%20receive%20a%2050%20percent%20discount%20on%20their%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-6-1710508295.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20opens%20to%20an%20exquisite%20view%20of%20River%20Krishna.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-6-1710508295.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-6-1710508295-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupload