div%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20would%20the%20village%20women%20be%20interested%20in%20this%20foreign%20concept%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20week%2C%2050%20women%20of%20the%20village%20responded%20to%20an%20ad%20that%20Sawant%20had%20put%20out%20in%20the%20local%20paper%20about%20her%20idea%2C%20effectively%20answering%20her%20question.%20Out%20of%20the%20group%2C%20two%20women%20raised%20their%20hands%20when%20Sawant%20enquired%20how%20many%20would%20like%20to%20turn%20their%20homes%20into%20homestays.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20families%20to%20show%20interest%20was%20a%20couple%2C%20Vaishali%20and%20Vijay%20Loke.%20Today%2C%20their%20homestay%2C%20%E2%80%98Pitruchaya%E2%80%99%20in%20Devgad%2C%20is%20a%20thriving%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20homestay%2C%20%E2%80%98Nandan%20Farms%E2%80%99%20at%20Sawantwadi.%20run%20by%20Amruta%20Padgaonkar%20is%20also%20amassing%20great%20love%20from%20tourists%20who%20are%20keen%20to%20spend%20their%20vacation%20at%20an%20authentic%20mud%20homestay.%20The%20locals%20weren%E2%80%99t%20left%20alone%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20intricacies%20of%20running%20a%20homestay%20business.%20Sawant%20hand-held%20them%20through%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20professional%20experts%20to%20come%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333328%2Fujjain-beautician-monisha-chhabra-broke-makeup-taboos-empowered-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrain%20the%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20was%20well%20aware%20that%20simply%20inviting%20tourists%20with%20the%20allure%20of%20an%20authentic%20stay%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20suffice.%20They%20needed%20more%20incentive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReviving%20crafts%2C%20traditional%20foods%20and%20nature%20tourism%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuppetry%2C%20once%20the%20pride%20of%20Sindhudurg%2C%20had%20assumed%20the%20status%20of%20a%20dying%20art%20form.%20The%20Pinguli%20village%20used%20to%20be%20a%20vibrant%20space%20where%20marionettes%20danced%20to%20tunes%20and%20dialogues%20narrated%20by%20their%20puppeteer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20was%20home%20to%20the%20Thakkar%20Adivasi%20community%20who%20were%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eparamparik%20kalakars%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(traditional%20artists).%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20the%20community%20received%20patronage%20from%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20who%20granted%20them%20land%20around%20Pinguli%20in%20the%20mid-18th%20century.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20community%20settled%20in%20the%20region%2C%20giving%20up%20their%20nomadic%20lifestyle%20to%20engage%20in%20performance%20crafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20with%20time%2C%20these%20crafts%20began%20to%20lose%20popularity.%20So%2C%20when%20Sawant%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20village%20while%20scouting%20for%20local%20crafts%20that%20would%20attract%20tourists%2C%20she%20was%20thrilled.%20In%20the%20months%20that%20followed%2C%20she%20set%20up%20the%20puppet%20museum%20%E2%80%98Thakkar%20Adivasi%20Lok%20Kala%20Museum%E2%80%99%20and%20got%20artists%20and%20designers%20on%20board%20to%20do%20a%20skill%20upgrade%20and%20design%20intervention%20workshop.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20intent%20was%20to%20train%20the%20puppeteers%20in%20how%20to%20organise%20the%20shows%20and%20create%20small%20products%20using%20their%20art%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20no%20one%20who%20visits%20Sindhudurg%20goes%20back%20without%20a%20visit%20to%20The%20Pinguli%20Arts%20Complex%20devoted%20to%20reviving%20and%20preserving%20the%20traditional%20crafts.%20On%20display%20are%20traditional%20art%20forms%20including%20%E2%80%98Chitrakathi%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20art%20of%20telling%20stories%20through%20pictures%2C%20%E2%80%98Kal%20Sutli%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20form%20of%20string%20puppetry%20and%20shadow%20puppetry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shadow%20and%20string%20puppetry%20have%20been%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20Thakkar%20Adivasi%20community%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpuppetry_11zon-1710845512-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345197%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShadow%20and%20string%20puppetry%20have%20been%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20Thakkar%20Adivasi%20community%20in%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Rashmi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20arts%20complex%2C%20Sawant%20was%20intent%20on%20helping%20the%20women%20earn%20through%20a%20craft%20they%20knew%20best%20%E2%80%94%20food.%20Under%20the%20banner%20%E2%80%98Hirkani%E2%80%99%2C%20Sawant%20also%20mobilised%20160%20SHGs%20through%20which%20300%20women%20were%20encouraged%20to%20produce%20squashes%2C%20pickles%2C%20etc.%20The%20women%20are%20now%20independent%20and%20these%20fares%20are%20sold%20at%20the%20homestays.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Sindhudurg%20model%2C%20Sawant%20headed%20to%20Pali%20in%20Rajasthan%20where%20she%20partnered%20with%2