0classroom%20environment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20FMP%20did%20was%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20lack%20of%20guidance%20through%20this%20gruelling%20examination%20process.%20%E2%80%9CAspirants%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20what%20they%E2%80%99re%20paying%20for%20when%20they%20join%20a%20coaching%20institute.%20They%E2%80%99re%20actually%20paying%20these%20institutes%20to%20guide%20them%20through%20a%20process%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20guide%20and%20plan%20%5Bthe%20course%5D%20themselves.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ravi%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20are%20given%20the%20choice%20of%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20attend%20coaching%20institutes%20or%20not.%20That%20choice%20did%20not%20really%20exist%20earlier.%20Much%20of%20the%20mentorship%20and%20guidance%20is%20in%20courses%20like%20our%20FMP%C2%A0%20just%20like%20the%20content%20is%20also%20available%20everywhere.%20If%20you%20use%20them%20both%20smartly%2C%20you%20can%20bypass%20the%20requirement%20of%20coaching.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20choice%20has%20to%20be%20with%20the%20consumer%20(aspirant).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20quit%20a%20desirable%20occupation%20to%20mentor%20UPSC%20aspirants%20and%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%20established%20by%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20comes%20from%20facing%20the%20drawbacks%20of%20the%20conventional%20school%20education%20system%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Kapoor%20runs%20a%20free%20course%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2