t%20wanted%20to%20be%20taught.%20I%20could%20have%20put%20up%20a%20video%20on%20YouTube%20but%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20teaching%20unless%20they%E2%80%99re%20(aspirants)%20actively%20involved.%20They%20need%20to%20generate%20an%20output%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20form%20of%20an%20essay%20or%20answer%20to%20certain%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20you%20do%20that%20for%20free%3F%20That%20was%20the%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20gave%20Ravi%20the%20time%20to%20write%20his%20book%20and%20develop%20his%20FMP%20was%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20in%20March%202020.%20This%20gave%20him%20the%20time%20to%20create%20and%20write.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%2010-12%20hours%20a%20day%20writing%20and%20creating%20content%20because%20there%20was%20nothing%20else%20to%20do.%20I%20was%20passionately%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20and%20realised%20the%20opportunity%20to%20quit%20placed%20before%20me%209-10%20years%20after%20joining%20the%20service.%20Also%2C%20my%20work%20was%20getting%20a%20good%20response%20and%20having%20an%20impact%20on%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20FMP%20consists%20of%20a%20lecture%20he%20posts%20on%20YouTube%20followed%20by%20an%20email%20which%20contains%20a%20carefully%20crafted%20assignment.%20Students%20have%20to%20complete%20it%20on%20the%20day%20they%20are%20given.%20If%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20finish%20the%20assignment%20on%20that%20day%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20next%20one.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20free%20email%20course%20where%20I%20help%20aspirants%20prepare%20for%20their%20UPSC%20exams.%20Upon%20joining%20this%20free%20course%20over%20email%2C%20I%20send%20you%20assignments%20every%20day%20with%20markers%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%20Once%20you%20finish%20the%20assignment%2C%20you%20email%20it%20back%20to%20me%20and%20I%20get%20to%20know%20whether%20you%E2%80%99ve%20done%20it%20or%20not.%20And%20I%20put%20you%20through%20this%20series%20of%20assignments%20and%20in%20that%20process%2C%20I%20not%20only%20provide%20the%20requisite%20study%20material%20but%20also%20psychological%20advice.%20The%20process%20I%20have%20established%20helped%20bring%20regularity%20and%20consistency%20to%20UPSC%20preparation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20facilitate%20this%20process%2C%20he%20employs%20Customer%20Relationship%20Management%20(CRM)%20tools%20which%20most%20businesses%20employ%20to%20sell%20their%20wares%20or%20services.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20use%20these%20tools%20with%20the%20aspirants.%20This%20was%20the%20innovation%20I%20adopted%20to%20facilitate%20learning.%20I%20used%20the%20sequential%20CRM%20emails%20and%20created%20a%20flow%20or%20a%20journey.%20Once%20you%20enter%20this%20journey%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20receive%20an%20assignment%20from%20me%20via%20this%20automated%20email.%20No%20one%20has%20used%20these%20tools%20for%20educational%20purposes%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20civil%20services%20exam%20contains%20three%20parts%E2%80%94prelims%2C%20mains%20and%20interview.%20Ravi%E2%80%99s%20FMP%20covers%20prelims%20except%20for%20CSAT%20maths%2C%20essay%20writing%2C%20current%20affairs%20and%20General%20Studies%20(GS)%20answer%20writing%20and%20ethics.%20It%20does%20not%20get%20into%20too%20much%20detail%20with%20optional%20subjects%20besides%20psychology%20and%20philosophy%E2%80%94subjects%20Ravi%20prepared%20for%20during%20his%20UPSC%20preparations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgoWy