%3EOne%20thing%20that%20Aravind%20and%20Vipin%20were%20sure%20about%20was%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20focus%20area%20and%20a%20problem%20they%20wanted%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20small%20town%2C%20what%20we%20understood%20was%20that%20India%20is%20not%20producing%20enough%20blue%20and%20white%20collared%20jobs%20for%20the%20educated%20youth.%20Another%20thing%20that%20we%20noticed%20is%20that%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20jobs%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20small%20towns%20become%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291959%2Fbest-products-from-northeast-india-sustainable-startup-entrepreneurs-small-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20entrepreneurs%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20them%20need%20mobility%20and%20they%20prefer%20two-wheelers%20as%20they%20are%20cheaper%20and%20faster.%20We%20realised%20how%20these%20small%20entrepreneurs%20need%20a%20two-wheeler%20that%20is%20efficient%2C%20electric%20but%20most%20importantly%20has%20ample%20amount%20of%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20became%20the%20primary%20focal%20point%20when%20the%20duo%20started%20to%20design%20their%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStylish%2C%20sustainable%20and%20green%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20why%20he%20named%20his%20company%20River%2C%20Aravind%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20like%20a%20river%20which%20is%20giving%20and%20helps%20others%20thrive%2C%20we%20as%20a%20business%20want%20to%20help%20other%20small%20businesses%20thrive%20with%20the%20right%20transportation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20utility%2C%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20as%20a%20company%20was%20the%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20s