osted%20on%20the%20website%20was%20written%20by%20a%20lawyer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20idea%20with%20Rest%20The%20Case%20is%20to%20provide%20vetted%20information%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20which%20the%20internet%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide.%20I%20have%20created%20one%20place%20where%20you%20can%20find%20everything%20from%20basic%20information%2C%20how%20to%20file%20a%20case%20to%20which%20lawyer%20to%20choose.%20We%20individually%20talk%20to%20clients%20before%20sharing%20their%20information%20with%20lawyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20was%20getting%20lawyers%20onboard.%20The%20then%2021-year-old%20would%20knock%20on%20their%20doors%20and%20explain%20her%20vision.%20Initially%2C%20many%20dismissed%20her%20or%20her%20idea%20as%20a%20mere%20%E2%80%98college%20project%E2%80%99.%20But%20she%20persisted%20and%20it%20paid%20off%20after%20she%20explained%20how%20this%20would%20be%20beneficial%20for%20everyone%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20show%20the%20lawyers%20our%20website%20and%20give%20them%20detailed%20explanations.%20Many%20were%20sceptical%20and%20believed%20that%20this%20project%20would%20shut%20down%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%20but%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20Slowly%20but%20surely%2C%20I%20onboarded%20about%2030%20lawyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20Yellow%20Pages%20for%20lawyers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4anwbMI3FP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4anwbMI3FP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E